Custom proprietary upstream artifacts

This package installs an unofficial Linux repack produced by:
https://github.com/Boria138/codex-app-linux

The upstream repository does not publish a repository-level license file.
The packaged archive includes Electron and Chromium license files, which are
installed under /usr/share/licenses/codex-app.

Use of the desktop application and bundled service functionality is subject
to the applicable upstream service terms.
